---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials for Photographers — SocialProof" description="Photographers: collect client reviews and display them on your portfolio site. SocialProof turns happy couples and clients into booked shoots — automatically." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/photographers">
<style>

    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .steps-section { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .steps-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .steps-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: left; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .quote-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #111; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .btn-nav { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff !important; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    footer a { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
  
</style>
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Let your clients' words book your next shoot</h1>
    <p>Photographers: automatically collect reviews from couples and clients after every session, and display them on your portfolio where future clients decide to hire you.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no card needed</a>
      <a href="/blog/how-to-collect-testimonials" class="btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-section">
    <h2>Why testimonials close bookings for photographers</h2>
    <p style="text-align:center;color:#555;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;">Your portfolio shows your style. Testimonials prove you're a real person to work with — that you put people at ease, you show up prepared, you deliver on time. That's what converts a browser into a paid booking.</p>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>💍 Wedding & portrait clients read reviews first</h3>
        <p>High-stakes bookings — weddings, newborns, headshots — require trust. Clients vet you thoroughly before enquiring. Testimonials on your site mean they arrive warm, not cold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📸 Your portfolio can't say everything</h3>
        <p>Beautiful photos show skill, but reviews tell the story behind them: how you made the nervous couple feel, how quickly you delivered the gallery, how professional you were on the day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🔗 One link — no login for clients</h3>
        <p>After the gallery delivery, send your collection link. Clients click, write a few sentences, and submit. No account, no app. Takes under 60 seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🖥️ Embed anywhere</h3>
        <p>Works with Squarespace, Pixieset, Showit, WordPress, or any website builder. Paste one line of code and your testimonials appear automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🌟 Highlight what matters</h3>
        <p>Approve reviews before they go live. Pin your favourites to the top. Show the testimonials that speak to your ideal client, not the most recent ones by default.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📈 SEO benefit too</h3>
        <p>Fresh, keyword-rich client reviews on your site help you rank for local photography searches — "wedding photographer [city]", "newborn photos [city]".</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="steps-section">
    <div class="steps-inner">
      <h2>Up and running before your next shoot</h2>
      <div class="steps-list">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Sign up free</h3>
            <p>Create your SocialProof account in under 2 minutes. Your personal collection link is ready immediately — no setup required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Send after gallery delivery</h3>
            <p>Add your link to your gallery delivery email: "Loved working with you — if you have 60 seconds, I'd love a quick review." That's it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Paste one snippet into your portfolio</h3>
            <p>One line of code in your site's footer or testimonials page. Reviews flow in and display automatically, always fresh.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Convert visitors to enquiries</h3>
            <p>Potential clients land on your site, read real words from real clients, and hit the contact button. Social proof does the selling for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-section">
    <blockquote>"My enquiry rate doubled after I added testimonials to my portfolio. People would mention specific reviews in their first message — they'd done the research before reaching out."</blockquote>
    <cite>— Wedding photographer, early SocialProof user</cite>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
    <p>Free forever for one widget. No credit card required. Takes 10 minutes to set up.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Get started free</a>
  </section>
</Base>
